node.text:
Instant classic. NARS Global Artistry Director @citizenjanes says of the @Erdem #SS22 beauty look: 

“Inspired by #Erdem’s images of Edith Sitwell and Lady Ottoline Morrell, I wanted to capture an ‘outside of their time’ view of beauty. With a focus on the eyes, the translucent, almost worn-in quality of the eyeshadow, set against the refined complexion, speaks to the ‘exist as you are’ sentiment of these two extraordinary women.”

Get the #ErdemSS22 look: 
Sheer Glow Foundation 
Radiant Creamy Concealer

#LFW

In the words of @AuroraJames. NARS sat down with the Creative Director and Founder of @BrotherVellies to talk #MetInAmerica. Captured during a beauty test with Global Artistry Director, @U.z.o. #MetGala #AuroraJames
 
Video: @Dapper.Studios

node.accessibility_caption: Photo shared by NARS Cosmetics on September 15, 2021 tagging @aurorajames, and @u.z.o. May be a closeup of 1 person.

node.text:
@AuroraJames, founder of @BrotherVellies and @15PercentPledge, wears a full face of NARS for #MetInAmerica. Global Artistry Director @U.z.o on the inspiration: 
 
“The beauty look combines elements of Aurora’s personal style with a 1960’s aesthetic, à la Jackie O—a nod to classic American beauty. Timeless black winged liner defines the eyes against a soft natural backdrop of luminous skin and a rosy lip.”
 
Get The Look: 
Pure Radiant Tinted Moisturizer
Soft Matte Complete Concealer
Climax Liquid Eyeliner
Orgasm Afterglow Lip Balm
#regram #MetGala
